data.description: This beautiful home sits on a corner lot, the kitchen features an island with smooth-top range, tile backsplash, solid surface countertops, two pantries and a two car garage. Separate dining room with separate room that could be used for an office space. All bedrooms upstairs. The Owner's Bathroom has a double vanity with an oversized tile shower. This lovely home has a wood-burning fireplace, huge laundry room, a large deck that overlooks the backyard, a privacy fence and  storage shed that stays with the home.
